column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "90745B5E4063D4972DFBF89B20201C35", "Huh? Is that right? I don\'t get it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "DAEDFEC442A06A8174B12B9C98CF5997", "I came here cuz I have a favor to ask. I want you to come to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "7DC656854FC30C0B45E5798619540B2A", "Well, you can open any shop you want.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "D1142A024C16E41259E829A4BA24F73A", "Wow, I always wanted to do that. Alright, I\'ll go!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "FBA09F2C4C9F1DA1633466806EB5F5C1", "OK, that sounds good. Then let\'s go now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "4500ECFD4AA80068A5B914B35E41B2F2", "A shop! Snow cones and ice cream. This is gonna be great!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2D20683A453CEC1AA94C20AFE0EA7057]", "AFC6F5CE492193610E25A08E347A71A9", "That Digimon can\'t stand cold very well!")
